Class CustomVcfIterator

java.lang.Object
no.uib.triogen.io.genotypes.vcf.custom.CustomVcfIterator
All Implemented Interfaces:
VariantIterator
public class CustomVcfIterator
extends Object
implements VariantIterator
This iterator iterates through a vcf file formatted according to the output of the Sanger imputation server.
